
'''Nkyifie (Bayere) Afahyɛ''' yɛ afehyia [[afahyɛ]] a ahenfo ne wɔn manfoɔ a wɔn wɔ Prang mpɔtam a ɛwɔ Pru atɔe mpesoa so wɔ Bono Apue Mantam mu, kane Bono ne Ahafo Manatam wɔ Ghana no<ref>https://visitghana.com/attractions/tags/nkyifie-festival/</ref><ref>https://www.peacefmonline.com/pages/local/news/201911/396281.php</ref><ref>https://www.graphic.com.gh/news/general-news/ngo-calls-on-chief-to-ban-wake-keeping.html</ref>.Wodi afahyɛ no bosome a ɛtɔ so nkrɔn no mu<ref>https://www.easytrackghana.com/cultural-overview-ghana-festivals.php</ref>. Afoforo kyerɛ sɛ wodi afahyɛ no wɔ bosome a ɛtwa toɔ no mu<ref>http://www.s158663955.websitehome.co.uk/ghanaculture/mod_print.php?sectionid=532</ref>. Afoforo nso di no wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so dubaako no<ref>https://www.nhoc.gov.gh/festivals</ref>.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi saa afahyɛ yi de kae nneɛma bi a esii wɔ tete<ref>https://www.ghanaconsulatedubai.com/tourism.html</ref>. Pru mano no nam afahyɛ no so sese won hwɛ wɔ afe a atwa mu no ho<ref>http://www.s158663955.websitehome.co.uk/ghanaculture/mod_print.php?sectionid=532</ref>.

